OL,3,CMore 'bang for our buck': Should
OL,4,CLondon's mayor have more power?
OL,6,FLondon should have more control over
OL,7,Fits destiny with greater devolution
OL,8,Fand more power handed to the Mayor of
OL,9,FLondon, a business group has said.
OL,11,FBusinessLDN, which represents some of
OL,12,Fthe capital's biggest companies, said
OL,13,FLondon had a huge tax surplus, which
OL,14,Fmeans the city pays more in tax than
OL,15,Fis spent here.
OL,17,FThe group said the way money was
OL,18,Fpartly spent in London was "bonkers"
OL,19,Fand devolution would help deliver
OL,20,Fbetter "bang for our buck".
