OL,9,FJohn Dickie.
OL,11,F"It's one of the richer regions of the
OL,12,Fcountry and some of that money should
OL,13,Fbe spent on general public services
OL,14,Felsewhere.
OL,16,F"But what is just bonkers is that
OL,17,Fgenerating that kind of tax surplus
OL,18,Ffrom one of the most vibrant economies
OL,19,Fin the world.
