OL,3,CMore 'bang for our buck': Should
OL,4,CLondon's mayor have more power?
OL,6,FLondon has had a mayor since 2000 to
OL,7,Frun key parts of the capital with a
OL,8,Fbudget of around #21bn to improve
OL,9,Feconomic and social development.
OL,11,FThe position is currently held by .
OL,13,FOther parts of the UK such as
OL,14,FManchester and Liverpool also have
OL,15,Felected mayors with varying degrees of
OL,16,Fpower.
OL,18,FIn London the mayor's focus is on
OL,19,Fissues such as transport, with the
OL,20,Fpower to set fares as well as policies
OL,21,Fsuch as the congestion charge and ULEZ.
