OL,6,F"We've had regional government now in
OL,7,FLondon for over 20 years. We've had
OL,8,Flocal government of one kind of
OL,9,Fanother in London for centuries.
OL,11,F"I think we've got the capabilities to
OL,12,Fmake really effective use of
OL,13,Fdevolution in the city. I think we
OL,14,Fcould drive jobs, growth and better
OL,15,Foutcomes if we more control over our
OL,16,Fown destiny.
