OL,6,FTony Travers from the London School of
OL,7,FEconomics said if London took more of
OL,8,Fits tax surplus it would rely less on
OL,9,Fgrants from central government.
OL,11,F"Probably the best way would be to
OL,12,Fallow London access to more of the
OL,13,Ftaxes that are set here, as happens in
OL,14,FScotland and Wales, you'd offset that
OL,15,Fby cutting central government grants
OL,16,Fto London," Tony Travers said.
